{"tid":592290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】傳特朗普考慮向中國科技電訊產品徵關稅","createTime":"2018-03-14T05:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T18:04:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5450d50d27b7d2205d16698efe8f11d36dc5750f","tid":592290,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/xitrump-13_CAzQx_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fxitrump-13_CAzQx_1200x0.png&h=ec20ee84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路透社引述兩名消息人士報道，美國總統特朗普打算向高達600億美元（約為4680億港元）的中國進口產品徵收關稅，特別針對科技和電訊產品。<br />\n<br />\n路透社又引述另直接了解政府想法的第三名消息人士表示，去年根據「美國貿易法」進行的「301條款」知識產權調查，關稅可能「在不久的將來」實現。這位人士表示，雖然關稅主要針對信息科技、消費電子和電訊產品，但針對的產品種類可能更廣泛，最終或者達到100種產品。白宮拒絕評論。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，消息人士稱特朗普針對的目標是中國高科技公司，藉以懲罰中國的投資政策 &mdash; 這些政策有效地迫使美國公司放棄其技術秘密，以換取被允許在中國經營，以及被視為損害美國利益的知識產權政策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0-%E5%82%B3%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%89%93%E7%AE%97%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%8A%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81%E5%BE%B5%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A8%258A%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585%2F&d=YFFXd4KYqv50WCakF7OTpi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=708150c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2